HEADWORD: Unsweat
<hw>Un*sweat"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>sweat</ets>.]</ety> <def>To relieve from
perspiration; to ease or cool after exercise or toil.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
